title: AOC E2470Sw Monitor Unboxing
description:
Today we have unboxing of the AOC E2470Sw Monitor this is a great value monitor and i would definitely recommend it to anyone. It features 2 HDMI ports and a VGA port which is rare for a monitor of this value. It has a full HD 23.6" screen.
